This dessert is perfection. It could not be any easier (and still be cooking), and it comes out light, creamy and simply delicious. I followed the directions exactly but was fortunate enough to strike upon Meyer lemons at the store, so I used them instead. So, so good. The zest sprinkled on top looked very pretty against the pale color of the posset. I will definitely make this again.

