Rating: 4
I would give this recipe 10 forks if I could. This was the easiest and probably one of the most delicious desserts I have ever made. If you like lemon and lime flavors, this is very subtle. If you love crème brûlée, this is creamier. I served this with fresh raspberries and blueberries on the side and it was spectacular. My guests were truly impressed and you will be too!

